'''MUBI'''（原名'''The Auteurs'''）是一家[[电影评论|电影评论]]网站，兼具社交网络、电影点播、电影数据库、在线杂志功能，被称为是“线上藏片室”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crunchbase.com/organization/the-auteurs |title=CrunchBase上关于MUBI的资料 |accessdate=2014-06-15 |archive-date=2019-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217043824/https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/the-auteurs |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及“影迷必爱”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.technewsworld.com/story/79060.html |title=If You're a Cinephile, You'll Love Mubi, if Not, It May Make You One-Technewsworld |accessdate=2014-06-15 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506215605/http://www.technewsworld.com/story/79060.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
==历史==
MUBI原名为The Auteurs，由[[土耳其|土耳其]]企业家[[埃菲·卡卡雷尔|埃菲·卡卡雷尔]]（Efe Çakarel）创立于2007年，是一个面向电影爱好者的社交网络<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cinevegas.com/blog/?p=687|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090113220031/http://www.cinevegas.com/blog/?p=687|url-status=|archive-date=2009-01-13|title=INTERVIEW WITH EFE CAKAREL OF THE AUTEURS | CineVegas Blog|date=January 13, 2009|accessdate=2020-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
卡卡雷尔称，他在[[东京|东京]]的一家咖啡馆里无法在线观看《[[花样年华|花样年华]]》后，便开始研究MUBI的[[商业模式|商业模式]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thenextweb.com/events/2012/06/23/why-its-so-hard-to-legally-stream-new-movies-online-a-chat-with-efe-cakarel-of-mubi/|title=Why it's So Hard to Legally Stream New Movies Online|first=Jamillah|last=Knowles|date=23 June 2012|website=TheNextWeb|accessdate=2020-07-23|archive-date=2019-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726212531/https://thenextweb.com/events/2012/06/23/why-its-so-hard-to-legally-stream-new-movies-online-a-chat-with-efe-cakarel-of-mubi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2010年，The Auteurs更名为MUBI<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://mubi.com/topics/why-did-we-change-our-name-to-mubi|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320170842/http://mubi.com/topics/why-did-we-change-our-name-to-mubi|url-status=|archive-date=2012-03-20|title=Why did we change our name to MUBI? - Film Forum on mubi.com|date=March 20, 2012|accessdate=2020-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

